        options: ["Benzodiazepines are contraindicated with all antihypertensive medications","STOPP recommends against benzodiazepines in older adults due to increased risk of falls, sedation, and cognitive impairment","STOPP only applies to long-acting benzodiazepines, not short-acting agents like lorazepam","Benzodiazepines are appropriate for insomnia in older adults if used for less than 6 months"],
